    <is_fda_regulated_device>No</is_fda_regulated_device>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study investigates the ability of cannabis to reduce chronic back and neck pain and to
      reduce sensitivity to an acute painful stimulus. Cannabis will be compared to both oxycodone
      and a placebo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study investigates the ability of cannabis to reduce chronic back and neck pain and to
      reduce sensitivity to an acute painful stimulus. Cannabis will be compared to both oxycodone
      and a placebo.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
